Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}打破了原有的安静祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}无所顾忌地大肆争执
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不给对方以喘息的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不给彼此以留下的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:39.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我一直喜爱你凝视我的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:47.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也始终怀念你带给我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那时整个世界只有我们二人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那时我们二人就是整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:01.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我还是会像过去一样颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:09.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我还是会为你放弃所有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:17.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我还是会像过去一样颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:25.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}只是为你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:32.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}We broke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Everything that was right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}We both enjoyed a good fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And we solved
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}All the holes we had to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}To make the other one leave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:39.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I loved the way you looked at me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:47.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I miss the way you made me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}When we were alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}When we were alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:01.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll shiver like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:09.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll leave him just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:17.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll shiver like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:25.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:32.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Like I used to
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚冬之山林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若传来低沉微弱 如细语之声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,则不久后 春虫将齐齐转醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此为众山之灵商议苏醒日期的响动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:33.38,title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)\p1\pos(1104,499)\c&H353664&}m 0 0 l -500 0 l -500 100 l 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:33.38,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)\pos(1091,302)}冬之底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下头疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想在惊蛰之前离开这条光脉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今年比预想的早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊蛰之后的虫大抵饥饿 很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然来信叫我了 但是眼下也没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不是什么急事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先避几天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天还冷着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 醒来之后就是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静得不太寻常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪早就该化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连颪笛都还在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经没有隆冬时的威力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面那座山已经没有雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为那边向阳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颪笛在迁徙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们正在北归
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座山上的颪笛群还没跟它们汇合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直在往下走 怎么又绕回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山封闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进山的时候没感觉到什么异常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬虫无法迁徙也是因为这个缘故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见见山灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点声音都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葎虫的气息也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}注：这种虫栖息在土中 类似山的神经
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光酒把山灵叫出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 都不知道发生了什么 还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的山灵…找到沼泽就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能老老实实地找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说山灵了 连只动物都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过仔细看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是到处都有山崩的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是秋天遭了台风吧 还是挺厉害的台风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山灵为了疗伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便封闭了山 让整座山冬眠了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对衰弱的生物而言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬眠可能让它们直接死去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面那座山已经是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这里却还没有复苏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说这座山只能等死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这么下去我也会被牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才有东西在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水面没有上冻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 喂 山灵阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把山封闭到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面早就是春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 它们聚集起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲着这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个沼泽怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在泥里 但是却能够呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们都睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光酒在不断涌出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在这里疗伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山还没有死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天…到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颪笛还在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们迁徙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山开放了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 这下子虫烟也全报废了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来得比想像中轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为山还没完全复原吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是山灵替我抑制了虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过连光酒都没了真是损失惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 衰弱的颪笛如果想要迁徙 光酒确实是必要的养分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我进山…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了搞到光酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都在山灵大人的掌控之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟春回大地了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬已去 山含笑 地似锦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 棘之道
